column5: Hey  Fellas,   been looking for a cover for my clam voyager.  BPS is sold out.   Le Barons dosnt carry it.   Anyone know where i might be able to find one?
I feel your pain...looking for a cover for my fish trap pro.  You'd think with ice season here that they shouldn't be to hard to get ahold of?  Nate
Try Fishing World in Hamilton.Thats were I got the cover for my Guide and it was $10.00 cheaper than Bass Pro.
Im gonna give fishing world a call in the morning.   Anyone know if Gagnons in shwa would carry it?
I am going to gagnons tomorrow i will have a look for you and let you know  rob

what a suprise that gagnons doesn't have it   ...Not sure how they run the store for 6 hours a day, closing befre most people even get off work and expect to make money and never have anything in stock for the current season, but hey they have all kinds of usefull bass gear for the season which is only 5 months away  Nate
Got it!!!!!!!!!!!!  fishing world in hamilton is fully stocked and a lot cheaper that most.   Havent been there in a few years but im gonna make sure to go a few times a year.
